title: Variety Bash: Paul to travel the Galaxie
text:
Variety Bash: Paul to travel the Galaxie Variety Bash: Paul to travel the Galaxie 3 hrs ago Read more: Central Western Daily 
A TEAM of drivers from Orange mining company Pybar are ready to hit the road for the annual Variety Bash, which leaves Sydney on August 2. HITTING THE ROAD: Pybar chief executive officer Paul Rouse is ready to drive from Bass Hill to Bunbury in his 1971 Ford LTD Galaxie with the Variety Bash on August 2. Photo: STEVE GOSCH A TEAM of drivers from Orange mining company Pybar are ready to hit the road for the annual Variety Bash, which leaves Sydney on August 2. Pybar chief executive officer and Pybash team leader Paul Rouse will take a 1971 Ford LTD Galaxie from Bass Hill in Sydney to Bunbury in Western Australia for the 4589 kilometre bash.   Central Western Daily.
